'''丙酮肟'''是一种有机化合物，是最简的[[肟|酮肟]]。其化学式为(CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>CNOH，外观为白色晶状固体，可溶于水、乙醇、乙醚、氯仿、轻石油，常用于[[有机合成|有机合成]]。<ref name=eEROS>Steven M. Weinreb, Kristina Borstnik "Acetone Oxime" e-EROS Encyclopedia of Reagents for Organic Synthesis, 2007.  {{DOI|10.1002/047084289X.rn00765}}</ref>

丙酮肟最早在1882年由德国化学家[[维克托·梅耶|维克托·梅耶]]及其学生制成并命名。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Meyer|first1=Victor|last2=Janny|first2=Alois|title=Ueber die Einwirkung von Hydroxylamin auf Aceton|journal=Berichte der Deutschen Chemischen Gesellschaft|date=1882|volume=15|pages=1324–1326|url=https://babel.hathitrust.org/cgi/pt?id=uiug.30112025692838;view=1up;seq=230|trans-title=On the effect of hydroxylamine on acetone|language=de|doi=10.1002/cber.188201501285|access-date=2020-12-26|archive-date=2022-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220120092145/https://babel.hathitrust.org/cgi/pt?id=uiug.30112025692838;view=1up;seq=230|dead-url=no}}  From p. 1324: ''"Die Substanz, welche wir, wegen ihrer nahen Beziehungen zur Acetoximsäure, und da sie keine sauren Eigenschaften besitzt, vorläufig Acetoxim nennen wollen, …"'' (The substance, which we – on account of its close relations to acetoximic acid, and since it possesses no acid properties – will, for the present, name "acetoxime," … )</ref>

== 制备 ==
丙酮肟可由[[丙酮|丙酮]]和[[羟胺|羟胺]]在氯化氢的环境下反应冷凝而得：<ref name=CRC>Handbook of Chemistry and Physics {{cite web|title=Acetone Oxime|url=http://www.hbcpnetbase.com/|accessdate=23 April 2014|archive-date=2008-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080523110822/http://www.hbcpnetbase.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=eEROS/>
:(CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>CO  +  H<sub>2</sub>NOH   →   (CH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>2</sub>CNOH  +  H<sub>2</sub>O
除此之外，也可以在过氧化氢的环境下，将丙酮[[Sohio法|氨解氧化]]而成。<ref name="Acetone Oxime Green Synthesis">Xinhua Liang, Zhentao Mi, Yaquan Wang, Li Wang, Xiangwen Zhang "Synthesis of acetone oxime through acetone ammoximation over TS-1"  Reaction Kinetics and Catalysis Letters Volume 82, pp 333-337. [http://www.orgmedchemlett.com/content/pdf/2191-2858-1-12.pdf] {{Wayback|url=http://www.orgmedchemlett.com/content/pdf/2191-2858-1-12.pdf |date=20120813083517 }}.</ref>

==用途==
丙酮肟是一种优秀的缓蚀剂，与常用的[[肼|肼]]对比，不仅毒性低，而且也更稳定。丙酮肟也用于酮、钴的测定，以及有机合成。<ref name="Acetone Oxime Properties">[https://link.springer.com/article/10.1023%2FB%3AREAC.0000034845.65961.3e#page-1 Acetone Oxime Properties] {{Wayback|url=https://link.springer.com/article/10.1023%2FB%3AREAC.0000034845.65961.3e#page-1 |date=20210630040210 }}, additional text.</ref>

